; Coverage test for xact.cc line 641
; The rounding adjustment loop skips @@ (total) cost postings
; 0.50 bread @ $3.99 = $1.995 exact, rounds to $2.00
; The @@ total cost posting should be skipped in the rounding loop

2024/01/01 Buy bread
    Expenses:Food    0.50 bread @ $3.99
    Expenses:Other    1 widget @@ $4.01
    Assets:Cash    $-6.01

test reg
24-Jan-01 Buy bread             Expenses:Food            0.50 bread   0.50 bread
                                Expenses:Other             1 widget   0.50 bread
                                                                        1 widget
                                Assets:Cash                  $-6.01       $-6.01
                                                                      0.50 bread
                                                                        1 widget
end test
